s: In May of 2005, I graduated from the Pennsylvania State University on a warm spring day. Prior to my graduation, my school’s Black Caucus held a “Sankofa” Kente Stole ceremony where all of us graduates received a Kente Stole with "Class of 2005" written on both sides.
